comment.body:
Method creates a new Property for the passed ComponentInfo.

@throws PropertyApplicationException if a Property with the same name already exists for the passed ComponentInfo.
@param pProperty Object describing the new Property for the passed ComponentInfo. The parameter must not be null.
@param pComponentInfo Object describing the ComponentInfo to which the new Property should be added. The parameter must not be null and it has to have a valid ServiceObjectID.
@return Property object describing the created object in the database. This object is not the same as the one that was passed to the method. The passed Property and ComponentInfo object should not be used any longer since its data was not updated. The method never returns null.
